    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/06dd6e4cdc904d38b9800a86400bcacf.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Looking for a unique dungeon crawler exploration game? You are in the right place.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey with &quot;Seeker of the Ruins,&quot; a captivating exploration adventure set in the forgotten depths of ancient dwarven ruins. As a courageous dwarf delver, your mission is to uncover long-lost treasures, unravel hidden secrets, and navigate the dangerous paths of the ancient realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.poster.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.webm?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6cf885879633836508e6063533d31688.mp4?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration: </strong>Venture your way through various epic ancient dwarven ruins. Find your way through the remains while collecting treasure and uncovering hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.poster.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.webm?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/ec3906ab56bd487da7e2ba8e8cc02371.mp4?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles: </strong>Navigate through environments filled with clues embedded in the surroundings. From deciphering runes  to interpreting the layout of a dwarven forge, in order to unlock forgotten chambers and treasure caches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.poster.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.webm?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/064dbdc98d82e85a9d62082d43cdac22.mp4?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>Hidden Areas: </strong>Discover secret rooms and concealed passages tucked away behind false walls and cryptic symbols. These hidden areas offer rare treasures, and shortcuts to the deeper mysteries of the ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.poster.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.webm?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/6dd8b41d99ffb7e8ffb1f1603d7fc728.mp4?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No-Combat &amp; Sneak: </strong>Navigate around the danger without ever drawing a weapon, relying instead on your wits, stealth, and timing. Outsmart ancient traps, environmental hazards, and dangerous monsters that challenge your intellect, while slipping silently past threats through shadowy corridors. Master the art of evasion and stay undetected as you explore the ancient ruins, ensuring your journey remains uninterrupted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.poster.avif?t=1749498344\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.webm?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208420/extras/10781657a2d5bf32c994fedc13e3a0c1.mp4?t=1749498344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Using Items to Your Advantage: </strong>Harness a variety of unique gadgets and mystical potions to bypass obstacles. Experiment by combining items to disarm traps, reveal hidden inscriptions, or get past enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready to delve into the depths and reclaim the forgotten legacy of the dwarves?</strong></h2>",
